Microarray data from the NCI-60 cancer cell line panel

Source: R/data.r
nci60.Rd

See ?ISLR::NCI60 for description of dataset.

nci60

Format

matrix with 6830 rows and 64 columns containing normalized gene expression values.

Source

ISLR::NCI60
